metadata.description: The Arrival series is an exploration of unknown places and spaces that human kind has yet to discover . These 1/1 Hand Painted works will be available to own not only digitally but physically a well , via a redeemable code in the hidden features section.
metadata.Redeemable Code: After purchase this code 358910 can be emailed to Theelightfederation@gmail.com as well as your wallet address to receive your physical 1/1 painting. Thank you :)
